# tests/markers_basic.crit — smoke test for `incr` + `if <marker>`.
#
# One agent, one marker. Agent increments the trail on its cell, then
# yields. On the next tick the `if trail > 0` branch should be taken.
# Exercises: marker declaration, ramp color, incr opcode, board-wide
# marker predicate, eager decay (disabled here via decay 0/1).

--- colors ---
ant:   (255, 180, 80)
trail: ramp (1.0, 1.0, 1.0) decay 0/1

--- agents ---
ant starts at (4, 4)

--- simulation ---
tick rate: 100ms

--- behavior ---
ant:
  incr trail
  if trail > 0:
    pause 3
    done
  pause 1
  done
